        <h2 class="font-effect-shadow-multiple">Our Website Design and Branding Strategy</h2>
        <p>
            When designing our website, we wanted to create a fun and playful 
            atmosphere that reflected the delicious and delightful nature of 
            our Bingfen dessert. We chose a soft pink color palette to complement 
            the sweetness of our dessert and evoke a sense of femininity and 
            elegance. We also wanted our brand name to have a memorable and catchy 
            ring to it, and so we decided to call it "Wendy's Bingfen." The name
             not only sounds like the well-known fast-food chain "Wendy's," but
              it also adds a personal touch by including the name of one of our
               founders. Overall, our website design is meant to be approachable 
               and inviting, encouraging visitors to explore our menu and try 
               out our delicious Bingfen for themselves.
        </p>
